1
00:00:14,090 --> 00:00:20,390
♪Suddenly, you showed up♪

2
00:00:22,150 --> 00:00:28,750
♪Who stole away those years♪

3
00:00:30,600 --> 00:00:37,320
♪Oh, night and day♪

4
00:00:38,760 --> 00:00:45,540
♪Oh, it's been a long time♪

5
00:00:45,930 --> 00:00:50,050
♪Pass through the bustling world
in the daytime♪

6
00:00:50,050 --> 00:00:53,880
♪Circumvent love at night♪

7
00:00:54,010 --> 00:00:57,760
♪Day after day, year after year♪

8
00:00:58,000 --> 00:01:02,040
♪I wake up and close my eyes
before it gets dark♪

9
00:01:02,040 --> 00:01:06,140
♪But when the day breaks into the night♪

10
00:01:06,140 --> 00:01:10,220
♪It makes me believe
that there's still love♪

11
00:01:10,220 --> 00:01:14,050
♪If you want it, if I want it♪

12
00:01:14,280 --> 00:01:20,800
♪It's a vow of night and day♪

13
00:01:26,520 --> 00:01:32,890
♪It's a vow of day and night♪

14
00:01:32,890 --> 00:01:37,200
[Blooming]

15
00:01:37,360 --> 00:01:39,920
[Episode 15]

16
00:01:46,720 --> 00:01:49,440
Will you do whatever I say?

17
00:01:49,760 --> 00:01:50,360
Of course.

18
00:01:50,360 --> 00:01:50,550
Of course.

19
00:01:51,830 --> 00:01:54,120
I need a guarantee.

20
00:01:59,630 --> 00:02:01,160
Here, read it.

21
00:02:03,080 --> 00:02:03,680
Come on.

22
00:02:07,190 --> 00:02:08,960
Zhao Tantan's Love Rules.

23
00:02:11,670 --> 00:02:12,550
Rule one:

24
00:02:12,800 --> 00:02:14,830
Report my whereabouts
to Zhao Tantan at all times,

25
00:02:15,190 --> 00:02:16,550
no hiding or deceiving.

26
00:02:17,440 --> 00:02:18,240
Rule Two:

27
00:02:20,520 --> 00:02:23,550
Work hard on alchemy and give
the elixirs to Tantan for selling

28
00:02:23,830 --> 00:02:26,190
until the Qingyuan Sect's

29
00:02:26,190 --> 00:02:27,110
little treasury is filled.

30
00:02:30,880 --> 00:02:31,750
Rule three:

31
00:02:31,830 --> 00:02:34,720
Don't compete with Tantan
for the Light of Qingyuan.

32
00:02:36,550 --> 00:02:38,240
Help her uphold justice

33
00:02:38,240 --> 00:02:40,270
and restore the reputation
of the Qingyuan Sect.

34
00:02:40,630 --> 00:02:43,360
Sworn by the disciple
of the Qingyuan Sect, Cui Chen.

35
00:02:46,270 --> 00:02:46,800
That's it.

36
00:02:47,030 --> 00:02:48,160
I've recorded it.

37
00:02:48,160 --> 00:02:49,190
Don't break your vows.

38
00:02:49,670 --> 00:02:50,550
As for this,

39
00:02:50,550 --> 00:02:51,830
you can keep it and memorize it.

40
00:02:56,520 --> 00:02:57,750
I also have a gift for you.

41
00:03:21,440 --> 00:03:23,630
It's beautiful, Cui Chen.

42
00:03:25,670 --> 00:03:26,960
Are you still calling me that?

43
00:03:28,550 --> 00:03:29,960
I remember you used to call someone

44
00:03:29,960 --> 00:03:31,800
very affectionately

45
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:33,520
with a special nickname.

46
00:03:36,360 --> 00:03:37,630
All right.

47
00:03:38,320 --> 00:03:39,080
Well,

48
00:03:39,830 --> 00:03:41,600
how about I call you Dabai?

49
00:03:41,830 --> 00:03:42,470
Dabai?

50
00:03:42,630 --> 00:03:44,910
My exclusive Dabai.

51
00:03:45,470 --> 00:03:47,440
Can you change it?
Qiu Yuebai also has 'bai' in his name.

52
00:03:49,190 --> 00:03:50,000
I want to call you that.

53
00:03:51,440 --> 00:03:52,270
All right.

54
00:04:06,320 --> 00:04:08,080
Mr. Qiu, what can I do?

55
00:04:09,190 --> 00:04:10,240
Go get ready.

56
00:04:14,110 --> 00:04:15,190
Tantan, Senior Mu Bai.

57
00:04:15,190 --> 00:04:15,880
Come over.

58
00:04:15,880 --> 00:04:17,720
The sugar pancakes
made by Hu Meng are delicious.

59
00:04:17,920 --> 00:04:18,880
Have some.

60
00:04:19,270 --> 00:04:20,000
Come on.

61
00:04:20,000 --> 00:04:21,350
Have a taste
of my niece-in-law's cooking.

62
00:04:21,720 --> 00:04:22,200
Uncle.

63
00:04:22,200 --> 00:04:23,440
What are you talking about?

64
00:04:23,600 --> 00:04:24,830
Your niece-in-law is...

65
00:04:24,830 --> 00:04:25,760
Huai Meng.

66
00:04:25,920 --> 00:04:26,790
Don't talk nonsense.

67
00:04:26,920 --> 00:04:28,000
That's what you wish for.

68
00:04:28,000 --> 00:04:29,070
What are you talking about?

69
00:04:29,390 --> 00:04:30,160
Xueyi.

70
00:04:30,550 --> 00:04:31,390
Take a look at me.

71
00:04:31,390 --> 00:04:33,550
Is there anything different about me?

72
00:04:38,040 --> 00:04:38,920
I know.

73
00:04:38,920 --> 00:04:40,600
Tantan, you've gotten stupid.

74
00:04:41,070 --> 00:04:42,790
Yes, that's the right direction.

75
00:04:42,790 --> 00:04:43,760
Take a closer look.

76
00:04:52,510 --> 00:04:53,200
You're so stupid.

77
00:04:53,480 --> 00:04:53,920
Well,

78
00:04:55,070 --> 00:04:55,640
Huai Meng.

79
00:04:56,440 --> 00:04:57,000
Take a look at me.

80
00:04:57,390 --> 00:04:58,760
Give me your hand.

81
00:04:59,640 --> 00:05:00,070
Here.

82
00:05:00,480 --> 00:05:01,160
It's fine.

83
00:05:01,320 --> 00:05:02,000
Stick out your tongue.

84
00:05:02,920 --> 00:05:03,640
It's good.

85
00:05:03,640 --> 00:05:04,480
Don't be so dramatic.

86
00:05:04,480 --> 00:05:05,270
It's nothing.

87
00:05:05,640 --> 00:05:08,040
It's so obvious. Why can't you see it?

88
00:05:08,880 --> 00:05:10,160
Look at Cui Chen.

89
00:05:17,550 --> 00:05:19,350
Are you kids

90
00:05:19,350 --> 00:05:20,600
sillier than me?

91
00:05:24,760 --> 00:05:26,440
Did Xueyi tell you

92
00:05:26,440 --> 00:05:28,880
that it'll show on your face
when you're in love?

93
00:05:29,880 --> 00:05:30,950
Let me tell you guys.

94
00:05:31,070 --> 00:05:32,230
They're

95
00:05:33,110 --> 00:05:34,040
in love.

96
00:05:35,760 --> 00:05:37,200
Tantan, you and Qiu Yuebai...

97
00:05:37,200 --> 00:05:37,670
No,

98
00:05:37,670 --> 00:05:39,480
you and Senior Mu Bai, are you in love?

99
00:05:40,390 --> 00:05:41,160
Cui Chen.

100
00:05:41,440 --> 00:05:42,510
Well done.

101
00:05:42,670 --> 00:05:43,670
Congratulations.

102
00:05:43,670 --> 00:05:45,000
If we go to the Yunlai Town
for noodles again,

103
00:05:45,070 --> 00:05:46,390
that would be two happy events.

104
00:05:48,790 --> 00:05:49,480
Look at her.

105
00:05:51,670 --> 00:05:53,230
We've been here for days.

106
00:05:53,600 --> 00:05:55,110
This matter is pretty much settled.

107
00:05:55,320 --> 00:05:56,230
What's your next plan?

108
00:05:59,510 --> 00:06:01,550
Don't worry about me. I'm fine.

109
00:06:01,760 --> 00:06:03,720
Being able to be there for him
in his last moments

110
00:06:03,950 --> 00:06:06,390
is already the greatest gift for me.

111
00:06:07,040 --> 00:06:10,440
Thank you for staying with me
in the past few days.

112
00:06:11,000 --> 00:06:12,270
Hu Meng.

113
00:06:15,390 --> 00:06:16,510
You're my best friend

114
00:06:16,510 --> 00:06:18,200
and a half-sister.

115
00:06:18,200 --> 00:06:20,600
No matter when and where,
I want you to be happy.

116
00:06:21,550 --> 00:06:23,270
Why don't you guys hug me?

117
00:06:23,270 --> 00:06:24,480
I want a hug too.

118
00:06:24,480 --> 00:06:26,040
All right.

119
00:06:26,880 --> 00:06:28,230
Don't be so sad.

120
00:06:28,230 --> 00:06:29,510
Mr. Qiu is right.

121
00:06:29,510 --> 00:06:30,760
What's your next plan?

122
00:06:31,640 --> 00:06:32,670
Keep looking for the lotus seeds?

123
00:06:34,670 --> 00:06:36,790
But there is no news
about the lotus seeds.

124
00:06:37,070 --> 00:06:38,720
Why don't we go back
to Yunlai Town first?

125
00:06:38,790 --> 00:06:40,040
There are more people
and more information there.

126
00:06:40,160 --> 00:06:41,270
It's easier to find out
about the lotus seeds.

127
00:06:41,720 --> 00:06:43,070
There isn't much information here.

128
00:06:43,390 --> 00:06:44,110
Okay.

129
00:06:44,600 --> 00:06:45,510
Let's go to Yunlai Town tomorrow

130
00:06:45,510 --> 00:06:46,950
and ask about the lotus seeds.

131
00:06:47,160 --> 00:06:48,640
We can also have some noodles
on the way.

132
00:06:48,720 --> 00:06:50,550
I need to update my Strange Tales
in the Secular World.

133
00:06:50,880 --> 00:06:52,230
The readers are looking forward to it.

134
00:06:54,600 --> 00:06:55,920
Aren't you the only reader?

135
00:07:20,390 --> 00:07:21,600
Miss Meng.

136
00:07:24,200 --> 00:07:26,230
How about you cover your face?

137
00:07:26,320 --> 00:07:27,790
I'm afraid they might...

138
00:07:28,670 --> 00:07:29,670
Don't worry.

139
00:07:29,830 --> 00:07:31,270
I'm your strongest supporter.

140
00:07:31,270 --> 00:07:32,920
I'll always protect you.

141
00:07:33,390 --> 00:07:34,880
It's not that dangerous.

142
00:07:35,110 --> 00:07:37,350
Just think of it as revisiting an old place
and meeting old friends.

143
00:07:37,830 --> 00:07:39,670
Tantan, did you hear that?

144
00:07:40,070 --> 00:07:42,200
That's the first criterion
of a good boyfriend.

145
00:07:42,440 --> 00:07:45,160
He treats your friends as his own.

146
00:07:45,720 --> 00:07:46,600
Miss Meng.

147
00:07:46,790 --> 00:07:48,510
Don't say such things out here.

148
00:07:48,760 --> 00:07:49,950
I'll be embarrassed.

149
00:07:55,640 --> 00:07:58,200
[Yunlai Inn]

150
00:07:59,720 --> 00:08:01,720
Let's go inside
and see what it's like now.

151
00:08:03,760 --> 00:08:05,480
But you were...

152
00:08:05,670 --> 00:08:06,390
It's okay.

153
00:08:06,880 --> 00:08:09,440
It's good to see who's taking my place.

154
00:08:09,640 --> 00:08:10,230
Let's go.

155
00:08:11,200 --> 00:08:12,640
Are you guys going in?

156
00:08:15,320 --> 00:08:17,160
Do you still want to hang out?

157
00:08:17,160 --> 00:08:18,510
There are too many of us.

158
00:08:18,510 --> 00:08:19,830
We'll cause them trouble.

159
00:08:19,830 --> 00:08:21,760
You're old friends catching up anyway.

160
00:08:21,760 --> 00:08:23,390
How about this,
you can chat as you want,

161
00:08:23,390 --> 00:08:24,480
and we'll stroll around.

162
00:08:24,480 --> 00:08:25,160
Don't worry about us.

163
00:08:25,160 --> 00:08:25,880
Yeah.

164
00:08:25,880 --> 00:08:28,350
I need to gather some material

165
00:08:28,390 --> 00:08:30,550
for the chapter about women in my book.

166
00:08:30,640 --> 00:08:31,480
We'll go to have some fun.

167
00:08:31,480 --> 00:08:32,320
Yeah.

168
00:08:32,470 --> 00:08:34,280
There are many strange things
on the street

169
00:08:34,280 --> 00:08:35,590
that I've never seen before.

170
00:08:35,590 --> 00:08:38,550
Okay, I know you three want to have fun.

171
00:08:38,550 --> 00:08:39,880
Go ahead.

172
00:08:40,230 --> 00:08:41,000
We're leaving.

173
00:08:42,910 --> 00:08:44,350
- Let's go.
- Xueyi, wait for me.

174
00:08:44,350 --> 00:08:45,110
Can you hurry up?

175
00:08:45,110 --> 00:08:46,080
Wait for me!

176
00:08:48,350 --> 00:08:49,110
Have you finished?

177
00:08:51,440 --> 00:08:52,520
Did you enjoy your meal?

178
00:08:52,670 --> 00:08:53,320
It's pretty good.

179
00:08:53,320 --> 00:08:54,280
Cui Chen.

180
00:08:55,230 --> 00:08:56,030
Do you feel

181
00:08:56,030 --> 00:08:57,760
that this place has become different?

182
00:08:57,760 --> 00:08:59,710
The people have become normal.
It's good.

183
00:08:59,790 --> 00:09:02,590
Yeah, it's completely different
from when we first came here.

184
00:09:02,910 --> 00:09:04,710
Guests, are you here
for a break or a stay?

185
00:09:08,350 --> 00:09:10,230
Zhong Zhuangyuan.

186
00:09:10,520 --> 00:09:11,670
It's you guys.

187
00:09:14,640 --> 00:09:15,760
Why are you here?

188
00:09:15,790 --> 00:09:17,000
Since you left,

189
00:09:17,030 --> 00:09:18,230
I've come to realize

190
00:09:18,520 --> 00:09:20,790
I used to think too optimistically.

191
00:09:20,920 --> 00:09:22,680
There's no such thing as a free lunch.

192
00:09:23,150 --> 00:09:26,000
So, I'm working here to earn
the traveling expenses

193
00:09:26,120 --> 00:09:27,150
for the imperial examination.

194
00:09:29,270 --> 00:09:31,440
What about the other scholars?

195
00:09:31,710 --> 00:09:33,480
They've also found good jobs.

196
00:09:33,590 --> 00:09:35,710
We're all grateful to you.

197
00:09:35,950 --> 00:09:37,320
This meal is on me.

198
00:09:37,510 --> 00:09:38,710
No.

199
00:09:41,590 --> 00:09:43,000
Cui Chen has money.

200
00:09:43,480 --> 00:09:44,240
Yeah.

201
00:09:44,680 --> 00:09:45,560
It's not easy to earn money.

202
00:09:45,680 --> 00:09:46,360
Keep your money

203
00:09:46,440 --> 00:09:47,920
for the journey
to the imperial examination.

204
00:09:48,480 --> 00:09:51,120
You helped me.
I can still afford a meal.

205
00:09:51,560 --> 00:09:52,360
Don't worry.

206
00:09:52,510 --> 00:09:54,830
The food here is different from before.

207
00:09:55,120 --> 00:09:56,120
It's delicious now.

208
00:09:59,920 --> 00:10:00,880
We'll eat here,

209
00:10:00,880 --> 00:10:02,000
but I'm not hungry now.

210
00:10:02,150 --> 00:10:03,560
We'd like some rooms first.

211
00:10:03,590 --> 00:10:04,590
- This way, please.
- No need.

212
00:10:05,480 --> 00:10:07,480
I've asked Mo Yan
to prepare a luxury suite.

213
00:10:07,750 --> 00:10:08,950
Let's go to the Qiye Inn.

214
00:10:09,070 --> 00:10:10,240
No, there is no need.

215
00:10:11,750 --> 00:10:13,920
Don't be angry, Qiu.

216
00:10:13,920 --> 00:10:15,390
It's not that I don't like the Qiye Inn.

217
00:10:15,440 --> 00:10:16,440
I just...

218
00:10:16,440 --> 00:10:17,510
We just don't need it.

219
00:10:18,190 --> 00:10:19,320
We won't stay for too long.

220
00:10:19,630 --> 00:10:21,240
Mr. Qiu, don't bother.

221
00:10:22,710 --> 00:10:23,750
Look at you guys.

222
00:10:23,920 --> 00:10:25,590
You have to make it sound so offensive.

223
00:10:26,070 --> 00:10:27,830
Mr. Qiu is hospitable

224
00:10:27,950 --> 00:10:29,920
because he treats you as friends.

225
00:10:30,510 --> 00:10:32,440
But then again,

226
00:10:32,630 --> 00:10:35,510
friends won't make a fuss
about such trifles.

227
00:10:35,680 --> 00:10:36,320
Right?

228
00:10:37,150 --> 00:10:37,830
Of course.

229
00:10:38,800 --> 00:10:41,070
I've got things to do. Help yourself.

230
00:10:42,360 --> 00:10:42,800
Qiu.

231
00:10:43,000 --> 00:10:43,680
Qiu.

232
00:10:47,480 --> 00:10:50,000
I wish it could be the same as before.

233
00:10:50,390 --> 00:10:51,120
What do you mean?

234
00:10:51,950 --> 00:10:53,560
What was so good before?

235
00:10:54,040 --> 00:10:55,480
It's already happened.

236
00:10:55,750 --> 00:10:57,560
Give him some time to process it.

237
00:10:57,560 --> 00:10:58,800
What are you so worried about?

238
00:11:02,630 --> 00:11:06,120
By the way, there's something strange
going on in Yunlai Town.

239
00:11:06,360 --> 00:11:09,150
There's a tavern
called the Shihua Pavilion.

240
00:11:09,240 --> 00:11:10,150
The owner is famous

241
00:11:10,390 --> 00:11:12,150
and her popularity is still rising.

242
00:11:12,320 --> 00:11:14,070
The strangest thing is

243
00:11:15,120 --> 00:11:16,270
she looks a lot like you.

244
00:11:17,710 --> 00:11:18,710
Me?

245
00:11:20,120 --> 00:11:22,560
When I first came to Yunlai Town,
a lot of people gathered around me.

246
00:11:23,040 --> 00:11:24,880
Did they mistake me for someone else?

247
00:11:25,390 --> 00:11:27,120
No wonder I found it so strange.

248
00:11:45,920 --> 00:11:47,800
Our relationship has been made public.

249
00:11:47,800 --> 00:11:49,190
There's no need to tiptoe around.

250
00:11:49,880 --> 00:11:51,390
Who's tiptoeing around?

251
00:11:51,590 --> 00:11:53,440
I just wanted to give you a scare.

252
00:11:53,630 --> 00:11:54,920
Well, Dabai.

253
00:11:55,190 --> 00:11:56,510
Instead of sensing the lotus seeds,

254
00:11:56,510 --> 00:11:57,950
you used your spiritual power
to sense my footsteps.

255
00:11:58,320 --> 00:11:59,710
What a waste.

256
00:12:01,070 --> 00:12:02,440
We've only been apart for a while.

257
00:12:05,440 --> 00:12:06,480
Do you miss me?

258
00:12:08,040 --> 00:12:08,880
Don't push it.

259
00:12:09,320 --> 00:12:11,920
I might make you vanish without a trace.

260
00:12:11,920 --> 00:12:12,680
I surrender.

261
00:12:12,680 --> 00:12:13,950
Let me go.

262
00:12:13,950 --> 00:12:14,590
Let me go.

263
00:12:18,070 --> 00:12:19,070
Good boy.

264
00:12:28,270 --> 00:12:29,070
Dabai.

265
00:12:30,040 --> 00:12:31,920
I want to go to the Shihua Pavilion

266
00:12:32,590 --> 00:12:34,680
and meet the person who looks like me.

267
00:12:38,000 --> 00:12:38,560
Okay.

268
00:12:38,560 --> 00:12:39,040
[Shihua Pavilion]

269
00:12:39,040 --> 00:12:40,950
Trust me.

270
00:12:40,950 --> 00:12:42,830
If you want to relax,
you have to come here.

271
00:12:43,070 --> 00:12:44,150
- Really?
- Yeah.

272
00:12:44,440 --> 00:12:45,680
Then I must check it out.

273
00:12:46,040 --> 00:12:46,830
Come on, let's go.

274
00:12:47,240 --> 00:12:48,590
We've walked too far today.

275
00:12:48,590 --> 00:12:49,560
I'm tired.

276
00:12:49,560 --> 00:12:51,390
Let's find a place to rest later.

277
00:12:55,750 --> 00:12:57,390
Did you have a good time today?

278
00:12:57,630 --> 00:12:59,360
We've had a great time.

279
00:13:01,270 --> 00:13:02,440
