562
00:25:30,270 --> 00:25:33,230
Don't try to fool me again.
I won't fall for it.

563
00:25:41,870 --> 00:25:44,990
First of all, a woman dolls herself up
for the man who loves her.

564
00:26:01,040 --> 00:26:02,960
Cui Chen, you're back.

565
00:26:36,390 --> 00:26:37,630
You've been working hard lately.

566
00:26:38,350 --> 00:26:41,440
I'll play some music for you

567
00:26:41,750 --> 00:26:44,080
so that you can relax.

568
00:27:42,960 --> 00:27:44,750
(To conquer a man's heart,)

569
00:27:45,470 --> 00:27:47,320
(you have to conquer
a man's stomach first.)

570
00:27:48,560 --> 00:27:50,510
(It makes so much sense.)

571
00:27:54,920 --> 00:27:55,750
What's this?

572
00:27:56,200 --> 00:27:57,990
It's called clay pot cooking
on the stove,

573
00:27:58,270 --> 00:28:00,040
abbreviated as clay pot.

574
00:28:01,840 --> 00:28:02,440
It's ready.

575
00:28:02,720 --> 00:28:03,560
The water is boiling. We can eat it.

576
00:28:03,920 --> 00:28:04,800
Don't we need to take the pot off?

577
00:28:05,870 --> 00:28:06,920
There is something you don't understand.

578
00:28:07,440 --> 00:28:08,560
The clay pot

579
00:28:08,720 --> 00:28:10,720
should be kept on the fire all the time.

580
00:28:10,840 --> 00:28:12,150
That way, you'll be able

581
00:28:12,150 --> 00:28:13,920
to eat hot food the whole time.

582
00:28:14,560 --> 00:28:17,800
We can also add new ingredients to it,

583
00:28:19,200 --> 00:28:20,840
and you won't have to wait.

584
00:28:23,800 --> 00:28:24,320
Try it.

585
00:28:32,110 --> 00:28:32,680
It's good.

586
00:28:42,230 --> 00:28:42,990
It's delicious.

587
00:28:43,230 --> 00:28:45,270
I have a talent for cooking.

588
00:28:45,840 --> 00:28:46,750
I'll make it more often for you.

589
00:28:47,350 --> 00:28:47,870
What's this

590
00:28:49,960 --> 00:28:50,870
called again?

591
00:28:51,230 --> 00:28:52,110
- Well...
- Clay pot.

592
00:28:52,440 --> 00:28:53,110
Right. Clay pot.

593
00:28:54,630 --> 00:28:55,320
But,

594
00:28:56,270 --> 00:28:58,870
it's a little hard to pronounce it.

595
00:29:00,040 --> 00:29:01,230
Why don't we just call it hot pot?

596
00:29:01,920 --> 00:29:02,870
What do you think, Dabai?

597
00:29:04,680 --> 00:29:06,390
It's good. Let's call it hot pot.

598
00:29:35,750 --> 00:29:37,110
(If she wants to do such things,)

599
00:29:37,600 --> 00:29:38,560
(just let her do it.)

600
00:29:39,390 --> 00:29:42,320
(However, I'm a little curious)

601
00:29:43,200 --> 00:29:45,560
(about what she will do next.)

602
00:29:49,560 --> 00:29:52,000
[I'll meet you by the lotus pond.
Lian Wen]

603
00:29:55,320 --> 00:29:56,600
Why isn't my food ready?

604
00:29:56,800 --> 00:29:57,800
It's too slow.

605
00:29:58,350 --> 00:29:59,680
Sir, here are your noodles.

606
00:30:00,040 --> 00:30:00,750
Thank you.

607
00:30:01,840 --> 00:30:02,320
Sir.

608
00:30:02,840 --> 00:30:05,040
Have you seen this person
in the portrait?

609
00:30:05,390 --> 00:30:06,040
No.

610
00:30:06,230 --> 00:30:08,440
Have you seen this girl in the portrait?

611
00:30:08,560 --> 00:30:09,320
- No.
- No.

612
00:30:09,470 --> 00:30:10,390
Her name is Tantan.

613
00:30:10,750 --> 00:30:11,440
No.

614
00:30:11,920 --> 00:30:12,440
No.

615
00:30:13,390 --> 00:30:14,150
No one has seen her.

616
00:30:14,350 --> 00:30:15,230
Thank you.

617
00:30:16,350 --> 00:30:17,470
Sir, here are your noodles.

618
00:30:19,600 --> 00:30:21,560
Well,
we've asked over a thousand people,

619
00:30:21,720 --> 00:30:22,750
and none of them have seen Tantan.

620
00:30:22,800 --> 00:30:25,040
What if she never came to Yunlai Town?

621
00:30:25,230 --> 00:30:26,040
No hurry.

622
00:30:26,560 --> 00:30:28,080
There are so many people
coming and going here.

623
00:30:28,510 --> 00:30:29,470
I'm sure we can find her.

624
00:30:31,840 --> 00:30:33,320
Look how busy we are.

625
00:30:33,720 --> 00:30:34,840
Do you still have time to chat?

626
00:30:35,200 --> 00:30:36,390
We've been working for so long.

627
00:30:36,800 --> 00:30:38,230
We have to find out where Tantan is.

628
00:30:38,270 --> 00:30:38,840
Yeah.

629
00:30:39,390 --> 00:30:40,920
We've earned money,

630
00:30:41,720 --> 00:30:44,150
but what if Tantan is living
on the streets,

631
00:30:44,200 --> 00:30:45,440
eating poorly?

632
00:30:46,110 --> 00:30:47,920
But you can't stop working.

633
00:30:47,920 --> 00:30:49,390
You can write a high-reward notice

634
00:30:49,560 --> 00:30:51,350
and post it at the door.

635
00:30:51,720 --> 00:30:53,600
People will come with clues.

636
00:30:54,200 --> 00:30:55,720
But we don't have money.

637
00:30:55,720 --> 00:30:58,470
If we can find Tantan, I'll pay for it.

638
00:30:58,870 --> 00:31:00,870
Mr. Crab, you're generous.

639
00:31:01,320 --> 00:31:03,080
You're the best boss I've ever seen.

640
00:31:03,720 --> 00:31:05,990
Stop flattering me and get to work.

641
00:31:09,990 --> 00:31:13,390
I'd be surprised if you can find her
with such a portrait.

642
00:31:13,960 --> 00:31:14,920
Wanna a steamed bun?

643
00:31:14,920 --> 00:31:15,630
It's hot.

644
00:31:15,630 --> 00:31:16,720
Be careful.

645
00:31:17,600 --> 00:31:18,320
Xueyi.

646
00:31:18,510 --> 00:31:19,040
Xueyi.

647
00:31:19,230 --> 00:31:19,680
Here.

648
00:31:20,150 --> 00:31:21,560
Miss, take a look.

649
00:31:22,040 --> 00:31:23,080
Have a taste of it.

650
00:31:25,470 --> 00:31:26,080
It's good.

651
00:31:30,040 --> 00:31:30,990
Look.

652
00:31:31,000 --> 00:31:32,320
[Crab Noodle Restaurant]

653
00:31:32,320 --> 00:31:33,510
I heard that their noodles
are really delicious.

654
00:31:33,560 --> 00:31:34,630
Crab Noodle Restaurant?

655
00:31:36,440 --> 00:31:38,040
Is there also a Crab Noodle Restaurant
in Yunlai Town?

656
00:31:38,320 --> 00:31:39,800
Could it be a fake?

657
00:31:39,960 --> 00:31:40,800
I don't know.

658
00:31:45,630 --> 00:31:46,600
Let's buy a bowl of noodles

659
00:31:46,800 --> 00:31:48,040
and let Uncle Zi Meng taste it.

660
00:31:48,750 --> 00:31:49,200
Okay.

661
00:31:49,200 --> 00:31:50,150
I'll go queue up.

662
00:31:52,110 --> 00:31:52,840
Qiu Yuebai?

663
00:31:53,510 --> 00:31:54,440
Are you also here for noodles?

664
00:31:55,510 --> 00:31:56,230
I'm just passing by.

665
00:31:56,320 --> 00:31:57,320
A group of Hu merchants
came from the west.

666
00:31:57,390 --> 00:31:58,440
I’m going to visit them..

667
00:31:58,990 --> 00:31:59,470
Hu merchants?

668
00:32:00,040 --> 00:32:01,230
What do they sell?

669
00:32:01,750 --> 00:32:03,510
Things like ivory, gemstones, and glaze.

670
00:32:03,920 --> 00:32:05,150
Some peculiar stuff.

671
00:32:05,440 --> 00:32:06,510
Would you like to come with me?

672
00:32:06,920 --> 00:32:07,920
Let's go too.

673
00:32:08,110 --> 00:32:10,230
But what about the noodles?

674
00:32:11,080 --> 00:32:12,350
We won't get our turn

675
00:32:12,350 --> 00:32:13,470
for another hour.

676
00:32:13,680 --> 00:32:15,560
Let's go take a look.

677
00:32:17,470 --> 00:32:19,960
Girls all like jewelry.

678
00:32:23,200 --> 00:32:24,230
Let's go.

